{
  "$comment": "Server-side RAG pre-routing (read hot per chat request). First matching category wins — order specific before broad. When a category matches, the Gatherlight server embeds/lists these docs in the plan prompt and the agent SKIPS the discovery-skill round-trips; 'lite': true additionally marks single-file template tasks that plan directly after the routed reading. Edit freely; a broken file falls back to the full agent-side gate.",
